#

Teriyaki Salmon Bowl with Steamed Broccoli and Jasmine Rice

$15.99
540 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

FishSoy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

Quick MealHealthyAsian-Inspired

Description

A simple yet flavorful dish featuring tender salmon glazed with homemade teriyaki sauce, served with perfectly steamed broccoli and fluffy jasmine rice.

Ingredients

  • Salmon fillet: 2 pieces (6 oz each)
  • Soy sauce: 1/3 cup
  • Brown sugar: 2 tablespoons
  • Honey: 1 tablespoon
  • Garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • Ginger (grated): 1 teaspoon
  • Broccoli florets: 2 cups
  • Jasmine rice: 1 cup
  • Water: 2 cups
  • Sesame seeds: 1 tablespoon
  • Green onions (sliced): 2 tablespoons
